exam situation, you don't

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:38.520
necessarily have to think
through everything, you can

00:09:38.520 --> 00:09:40.930
just use this very quick way
to figure out the number of

00:09:40.930 --> 00:09:42.830
hybrid orbitals that you need.

00:09:42.830 --> 00:09:47.450
And what we just said is that
any time we need two hybrid

00:09:47.450 --> 00:09:54.990
