to worry about most

00:20:03.870 --> 00:20:07.040
of our pets at home.

00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:10.040
Unless you have a guinea pig
and they don't, in fact,

00:20:10.040 --> 00:20:13.870
biosynthesize vitamin C, so I
think they supplement most

00:20:13.870 --> 00:20:16.240
