00:45:02.800 --> 00:45:05.520
we're talking about an element
in their most stable state,

00:45:05.520 --> 00:45:06.690
it's going to be zero.

00:45:06.690 --> 00:45:09.040
That's going to be the delta
h of formation, there

00:45:09.040 --> 00:45:11.650
is none, it's zero.

00:45:11.650 --> 00:45:15.820
We can also look up what it was
for sugar, for glucose, c

00:45:15.820 --> 00:45:18.050
6 h 12 o 6.

00:45:18.050 --> 00:45:22.406
So that coming from its most
stable forms, it was the most

00:45:22.406 --> 00:45:25.880
pure form of the elements, is
