00:45:25.880 --> 00:45:27.600
kilojoules per mole.

00:45:27.600 --> 00:45:31.060
All of this information has
been tabulated and is in

00:45:31.060 --> 00:45:33.380
tables, you can refer to them,
and they're also in the back

00:45:33.380 --> 00:45:35.940
of your textbook, so you can
